{
    "a_galaxy_workflow": "true",
    "annotation": "This workflow performs taxonomic classification of an input sequence collection (e.g., bins from SemiBin2 or MetaBat) using GTDB-Tk and kMetaShot (optional). GTDB-Tk taxonomy is mapped to NCBI taxIDs and names to reconcile differences between NCBI/GTDB taxonomies.\n",
